    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Yes, this is described in the documentation. You have to use the <a href=\"https://github.com/mockito/mockito/blob/master/src/main/java/org/mockito/InOrder.java\" rel=\"noreferrer\">InOrder</a> class.</p>\n\n<p>Example (assuming two mocks already created):</p>\n\n<pre><code>InOrder inOrder = inOrder(serviceAMock, serviceBMock);\n\ninOrder.verify(serviceAMock).methodOne();\ninOrder.verify(serviceBMock).methodTwo();\n</code></pre>\n"
