    "answer_id" : 76550262,
    "question_id" : 21901368,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>When verifying the invocation order of a single method call with different arguments it's essentially the same:</p>\n<pre><code>ServiceClass myMock = mock(ServiceClassA.class);\n\nInOrder inOrder = inOrder(myMock);\n\ninOrder.when(myMock).myMethod(42);\ninOrder.when(myMock).myMethod(69);\n</code></pre>\n"
